04:58:29.180 --> 04:58:31.360
Labeldrucker, wo ich Adressen

04:58:31.360 --> 04:58:31.840
und sowas

04:58:31.840 --> 04:58:34.960
raushaue.

04:58:34.960 --> 04:58:38.580
